    <title>hexo win10下安装</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2017/05/03/hexo-win10%E4%B8%8B%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2017/05/03/hexo-win10下安装/</id>
    <published>2017-05-03T06:22:52.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-05-04T05:28:27.196Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>hexo 博客在windows 10下快速搭建步骤：</p>
<h3 id="0x1-安装tortoisegit。"><a href="#0x1-安装tortoisegit。" class="headerlink" title="0x1 安装tortoisegit。"></a>0x1 安装tortoisegit。</h3><blockquote><p>1.1 新建Repository yourname.github.io<br>1.2 开通 page 服务。<br>1.3 本地新建index.html(hello world) push到username.github.io<br> <figure class="highlight html"><figcaption><span>index.html</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>yourname’s Blog<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">         <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>Hello World<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">         <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>I’m hosted with GitHub Paes<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>1.4 访问yourname.github.io 可以看到helloworld。</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="0x2-安装nodejs"><a href="#0x2-安装nodejs" class="headerlink" title="0x2 安装nodejs"></a>0x2 安装nodejs</h3><blockquote>
<p>2.1 <a href="http://nodejs.org" target="_blank" rel="external">http://nodejs.org</a> 下载安装文件，点击安装。<br>2.2 配置npm的全局模块的存放路径以及cache的路:<br> <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> prefix <span class="string">"C:\Program Files\nodejs\node_global"</span> </div><div class="line">$ npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> cache <span class="string">"C:\Program Files\nodejs\node_cache"</span> </div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>2.3 设置环境变量 NODEPATH=C:\Program Files\nodejs\node_global </p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="0x3-安装hexo"><a href="#0x3-安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="0x3 安装hexo"></a>0x3 安装hexo</h3><blockquote>
<p>3.1 新建一个hexo目录，不带中文，不带空格。<br> 3.2 打开git bash，cd到hexo。</p>
<h4 id="方法A-使用默认源安装"><a href="#方法A-使用默认源安装" class="headerlink" title="方法A (使用默认源安装)"></a>方法A (使用默认源安装)</h4>   <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-cli -g </div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p> 方法A可执行，则忽略以下方法B。</p>
<h4 id="方法B-使用淘宝源安装"><a href="#方法B-使用淘宝源安装" class="headerlink" title="方法B 使用淘宝源安装"></a>方法B 使用淘宝源安装</h4>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install -g hexo-cli --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org </div><div class="line">$ cnpm install  //淘宝镜像安装</div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo --save </div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>3.3 查看本地hexo是否安装正确<br>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo -v</div><div class="line">$ hexo init //如果出错忽略，直接输入下一步命令会自动安装需要的组件。</div><div class="line">$ hexo g</div><div class="line">$ hexo s //浏览器打开  http://localhost:4000/</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="0x4-修改hexo主题"><a href="#0x4-修改hexo主题" class="headerlink" title="0x4 修改hexo主题"></a>0x4 修改hexo主题</h3><blockquote>
<p>在<a href="https://hexo.io/themes/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://hexo.io/themes/</a> 查找中意的theme项目, 点进去找到 github项目,<br>  之后按照theme 提示安装。<br>  示例安装 //<a href="https://github.com/chaooo/hexo-theme-BlueLake" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/chaooo/hexo-theme-BlueLake</a><br>     <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/chaooo/hexo-theme-BlueLake.git themes/BlueLake</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="0x5-安装完成后分别执行"><a href="#0x5-安装完成后分别执行" class="headerlink" title="0x5 安装完成后分别执行"></a>0x5 安装完成后分别执行</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo clean</div><div class="line">$ hexo g</div><div class="line">$ hexo d</div><div class="line">$ hexo s //浏览器打开  http://localhost:4000/ 已经是新主题了</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="0x6-配置Deployment"><a href="#0x6-配置Deployment" class="headerlink" title="0x6 配置Deployment"></a>0x6 配置Deployment</h3><blockquote>
<p>6.1 git bash配置身份信息:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ git config --global user.name <span class="string">"yourname"</span></div><div class="line">$ git config --global user.email <span class="string">"youremail"</span> </div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>  6.2 在_config.yml文件中，找到Deployment，然后按照如下修改：<br>  <figure class="highlight xml"><figcaption><span>_comfig.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">deploy:</div><div class="line">  type: git</div><div class="line">  repo: git@github.com:yourname/yourname.github.io.git</div><div class="line">branch: master</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure> 上面的四个:对齐且type: repo: branch: 后面有空格.<br>  6.3 安装所需插件<br>  <figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
  6.4 发布项目
  <figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo d //出现错误信息则说明git bash没有配置ssh。</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="0x7-配置ssh"><a href="#0x7-配置ssh" class="headerlink" title="0x7 配置ssh"></a>0x7 配置ssh</h3>   <blockquote><p>7.1 在gitbash中执行ssh-keygen<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">“yourname@xxx.com”</span> </div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>   7.2 打开 C:\Users\username.ssh\id_rsa.pub，复制字符串。<br>   7.3 登录<a href="http://github.com" target="_blank" rel="external">http://github.com</a> 。点击右上角用户图片右边小三角，打开Settings。<br>   <img src="/content/images/hexo-win10下安装/github_setting.jpg" alt="github setting" width="70%" height="70%"><br>   7.4 右边菜单点击”SSH and GPG keys”-&gt;New SSH key-&gt;title文本框输入文字,key文本框右键粘贴-&gt;保存。</p>
</blockquote>
<p>   <img src="/content/images/hexo-win10下安装/ssh_keys.jpg" alt="add ssh keys"></p>
<h3 id="0x8-发布项目"><a href="#0x8-发布项目" class="headerlink" title="0x8 发布项目"></a>0x8 发布项目</h3>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo d //github 已更新，在ie中打开 yourname.github.io。</div><div class="line">$ hexo d -g //如果服务端页面未更新的时候，加-g命令。</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
    
